Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.40,0:00:04.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.60,0:00:07.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人在三尾的腹中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.56,0:00:29.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些怪胎 还真像小孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.90,0:00:35.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总感觉心情舒畅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.98,0:00:38.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恍若重生一般
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.61,0:00:40.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前筋疲力尽的感觉也消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.04,0:00:42.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不仅如此
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.75,0:00:45.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得力量在源源不断地涌出
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.01,0:00:47.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.07,0:00:50.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论如何都要从木叶的手中夺回幽鬼丸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.90,0:00:54.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心 四眼君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.22,0:00:57.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以目前的状态而言 我们绝不会输给任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.08,0:00:59.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便是红莲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.76,0:01:02.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就好好表现一番吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.00,0:01:05.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然并不抱太大的期望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.55,0:01:10.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此话当真
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.71,0:01:13.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按幽鬼丸所说的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.19,0:01:17.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晶遁忍者红莲还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.38,0:01:21.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人和红莲一起被三尾吞入腹中了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.98,0:01:24.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从我们如此搜索都毫无踪迹来看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.51,0:01:27.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此言的确不虚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.83,0:01:30.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 为什么这么肯定红莲没事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.41,0:01:34.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是红莲姐给我做的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.22,0:01:37.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果红莲姐出事的话 这个也会破裂的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.95,0:01:39.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.42,0:01:43.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 这也只能证明红莲平安无事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.06,0:01:46.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人的安危依旧不得而知
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.02,0:01:50.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确 谁也不知道三尾的腹中会发生些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.57,0:01:52.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便都平安无事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.75,0:01:55.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但鸣人还是会和晶遁忍者遭遇的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.41,0:01:59.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两人很可能会大战一番 以决雌雄
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.42,0:02:01.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么…鸣人会…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.21,0:02:04.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在下定论毫无意义
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.35,0:02:05.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能相信他还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.78,0:02:07.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先要找到三尾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.54,0:02:10.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以试试
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.44,0:02:13.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能找到三尾吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:17.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然无法确切地知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.34,0:02:18.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但能隐约感觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.47,0:02:22.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可即便找到三尾 下面又该如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.48,0:02:25.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再进行一次封印术
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.32,0:02:28.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样吧 先尝试在这段时间里营救鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.63,0:02:30.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在三尾出现的地点集合
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.35,0:02:34.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和 为防找到鸣人的同时撞上红莲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.40,0:02:36.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和志乃同行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.75,0:02:38.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐井在上空伺机行事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.62,0:02:41.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其余人员警戒四周
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.18,0:04:24.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对手是兜 天知道他会搞什么小动作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.78,0:04:26.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.60,0:04:30.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们也要多加小心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.48,0:04:33.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,志乃 差不多该出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.94,0:04:34.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.38,0:04:45.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 我们封印班就紧随在最后吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.99,0:04:48.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽量在不刺激三尾的状态下 悄悄潜行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.61,0:04:49.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.55,0:04:53.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.88,0:05:28.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.42,0:05:30.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被摆了一道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.91,0:05:32.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影分身全灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.55,0:05:33.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.41,0:05:36.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个声音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.72,0:05:38.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.65,0:05:41.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙了啊…这种数量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.93,0:05:51.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.52,0:06:01.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有那种大家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.47,0:06:04.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不得不战了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.90,0:06:07.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可你这身体状态想怎么打啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.34,0:06:09.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你说我们能逃去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.24,0:06:14.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确是走投无路…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.47,0:06:18.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晶遁.六角手里剑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.97,0:06:25.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 完全没用嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.86,0:06:27.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边我先挡着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.41,0:06:29.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你伺机逃走吧 知道了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.62,0:06:30.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.43,0:06:50.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.48,0:06:52.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红莲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.97,0:06:54.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.74,0:07:04.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.61,0:07:08.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.58,0:07:10.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影分身之术
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.16,0:07:13.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快到我背上来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.41,0:07:15.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这怎么行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.30,0:07:16.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.07,0:07:18.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.36,0:07:19.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的自尊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.97,0:07:20.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是白痴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.95,0:07:23.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是在意那些俗事的场合吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.63,0:07:26.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白痴 放我下来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.00,0:07:27.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我老实点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.66,0:07:31.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.13,0:07:42.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.10,0:07:57.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道小樱她们进展是否顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.42,0:07:59.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人要是平安无事就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.95,0:08:02.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系 肯定没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.63,0:08:07.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他可是一个让我想要与之认真较量的人物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.06,0:08:10.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 赤丸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.55,0:08:14.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来是敌人大驾光临了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.07,0:08:17.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来得正好 正是我热血沸腾的时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.92,0:08:20.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将对鸣人的思念寄托在这拳头之上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.64,0:08:32.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么又是你们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.25,0:08:33.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亏你能发现我们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.64,0:08:37.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便消除了踪迹和气味 但那股杀气是无法隐匿的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.45,0:08:39.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,输过一次的手下败将休想赢我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.72,0:08:41.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少狗眼看人低了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.28,0:08:43.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已经脱胎换骨了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.04,0:08:45.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔烟丸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.71,0:08:48.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就无法接近了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.70,0:08:50.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要比炮弹量的话 我可不会输哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.41,0:08:53.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.63,0:09:00.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的苦无都…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.33,0:09:03.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现身吧 烟龙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.71,0:09:19.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.32,0:09:22.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉到了 就在这下面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.32,0:09:25.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 封印班 准备…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.30,0:09:26.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.82,0:09:28.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有出口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.53,0:09:31.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红莲姐他们正在找寻出口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.36,0:09:32.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.42,0:09:36.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能从外部打开的话 就能变成出口了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.61,0:09:38.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.51,0:09:42.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 看来有必要先调查一下湖底
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.17,0:09:43.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山茶花
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.51,0:09:45.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收集多点山茶花过来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.86,0:09:46.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山茶花
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.97,0:09:52.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么救我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.95,0:09:54.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我要问的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.79,0:09:56.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.51,0:10:00.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你现在去了西天也取不到西经来救我的命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.15,0:10:01.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.39,0:10:03.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是在依赖我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.75,0:10:06.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 你的伤势如何了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.93,0:10:12.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不准碰我 等离开了这里 你我就是敌人了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.20,0:10:15.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随便你啦 不过我是不会把幽鬼丸交给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.30,0:10:18.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么如此执着于幽鬼丸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.78,0:10:20.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前不是已经说过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.69,0:10:22.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管有何隐情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.45,0:10:25.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你所跟随的大蛇丸是个大坏蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.09,0:10:28.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正你肯定也是被利用了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.91,0:10:30.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就跟那家伙一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.04,0:10:33.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.14,0:10:38.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 你和大蛇丸绝非是幽鬼丸的归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.37,0:10:41.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去前方稍作侦查
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.14,0:10:44.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影分身侦察不太方便
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.91,0:10:55.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 看起来相当深呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.27,0:10:57.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.36,0:11:08.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.96,0:11:13.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙 难道又是那些家伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.22,0:11:22.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁啊 为什么会出现在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.64,0:11:26.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.04,0:11:31.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助 为什么你会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.67,0:11:51.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.52,0:11:54.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有心里话想跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.49,0:11:58.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手啊 佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.98,0:12:12.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是三尾之雾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.68,0:12:14.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.17,0:12:25.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这雾能将人内心深处的弱点幻化并显现出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.15,0:12:27.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我进去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.66,0:12:29.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也将要面对这些
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.70,0:12:33.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助 别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.91,0:13:03.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是您…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.78,0:13:09.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对您做了无可挽回的错事…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.01,0:13:11.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望能得到您的原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.72,0:13:14.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便现在已经毫无意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.48,0:13:18.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是即便赌上性命 我也会誓死守护您的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.05,0:13:42.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助 你可是有归宿的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.65,0:13:44.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你忘了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.19,0:13:47.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.60,0:13:52.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开 快放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.87,0:13:56.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作点 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.40,0:13:58.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你所见到的都是幻觉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.92,0:14:13.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得救了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.13,0:14:16.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是见到宇智波佐助了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.73,0:14:20.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也知道佐助吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.21,0:14:25.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在大蛇丸大人那遇见过 是个恐怖的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.17,0:14:28.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙没事吧 还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.81,0:14:31.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要问这些
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.66,0:14:33.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那还用说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.26,0:14:35.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是我们的同伴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.56,0:14:37.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝对要将他带回来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.92,0:14:41.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要告诉佐助 他还有着归宿所在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.24,0:14:46.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你当真如此想带回宇智波佐助吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.06,0:14:47.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.40,0:14:49.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.60,0:14:56.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇智波佐助…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.90,0:14:59.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙真是个白痴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.77,0:15:03.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不由分说地想去帮助那个佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.51,0:15:09.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么可笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.54,0:15:12.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从未见过你这样的白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.18,0:15:13.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 突然间…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.44,0:15:15.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笑得我肚子疼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.22,0:15:17.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的疼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.62,0:15:18.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.82,0:15:28.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.16,0:15:31.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是幽鬼丸所说的通往异世界的入口
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.71,0:15:37.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换言之 只要捅破那层膜 就能制造出出口
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.60,0:15:43.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.66,0:15:47.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷切
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.35,0:15:53.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 雾突然间…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.97,0:15:55.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说向外飘散了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.42,0:15:58.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.60,0:16:00.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下真是走投无路了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.32,0:16:03.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 又来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.62,0:16:05.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是些纠缠不清的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.01,0:16:07.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来一击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.01,0:16:11.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快给我回来 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.01,0:16:21.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备完成
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.09,0:16:23.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.76,0:16:43.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人 有件事我必须告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.81,0:16:46.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事啊 在这节骨眼上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.25,0:16:49.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幽鬼丸的母亲不是死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.58,0:16:53.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凶手正是我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.77,0:16:55.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.21,0:16:58.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时 为了建立音忍村
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.28,0:17:02.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大蛇丸大人命令我去袭击幽鬼丸的村子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.34,0:17:07.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 精疲力竭的我在那里倒下了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.75,0:17:22.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而她却救了身为敌人的我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.35,0:17:28.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃吧 趁我现在还能当没看见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.68,0:17:48.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要背叛我吗 红莲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.37,0:17:54.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我却…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.62,0:17:59.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一心为了得到大蛇丸大人的认可
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.61,0:18:00.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而将她…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.64,0:18:17.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我将那时的记忆和感情封印了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.87,0:18:21.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却在跟幽鬼丸相遇后全部苏醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.10,0:18:24.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你才对幽鬼丸…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.95,0:18:26.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正如你所说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.34,0:18:31.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给幽鬼丸的心灵造成无以弥补伤害的我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.09,0:18:34.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有资格去保护那个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.91,0:18:35.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红莲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.29,0:18:37.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经快不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.86,0:18:41.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 现在即便拼上性命也要保护你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.04,0:18:44.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要给我活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.45,0:18:45.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幽鬼丸就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.98,0:18:48.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些话真够肉麻的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.75,0:18:50.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管以前发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.13,0:18:51.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的你已经脱胎换骨了 不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.52,0:18:53.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.33,0:18:59.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山茶花
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.56,0:19:14.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幽鬼丸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.16,0:19:19.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙在为我们引路
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.54,0:19:21.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.06,0:19:33.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 就是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.04,0:19:46.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会让你死在这的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.34,0:19:48.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要一起回去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.50,0:21:38.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太失策了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.54,0:21:41.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万一木叶的封印成功的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.99,0:21:46.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大蛇丸大人未来的战斗力将会有很大的变化
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.11,0:21:49.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要避免那样的事发生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.78,0:21:50.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事已至此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.11,0:21:54.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便是舍弃幽鬼丸这颗棋子 也是情非得已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.51,0:21:58.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要拼尽全力去搅乱木叶的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.85,0:22:02.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 咒印的逆袭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.26,0:22:08.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来收录的场景是24小时以内
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.96,0:22:13.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,潜入敌人据点的惊险片段
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.98,0:22:13.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话筒不出声啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.83,0:22:18.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 大和队长
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.23,0:22:20.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剧本不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.53,0:22:22.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又给忘了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.37,0:22:23.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是第二回了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.70,0:22:24.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不是的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.94,0:22:28.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 今天可是绝不能犯错的场合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.02,0:22:30.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以为防万一 还做了V检查
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.35,0:22:31.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顺便一提
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.15,0:22:35.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所谓V检查 就是一边观看一边演练台词
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.49,0:22:38.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.42,0:22:41.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来木叶的上忍也堕落了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.70,0:22:43.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…也不是这么回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.07,0:22:44.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太逊了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.68,0:22:45.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我算是看错人了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.09,0:22:46.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是就是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.01,0:22:48.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了啦 不要说这种话了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.09,0:22:51.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法了 我的借给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.34,0:22:52.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡卡西前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.47,0:22:55.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不就是我的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.33,0:22:58.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.27,0:23:00.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还被涂得乱七八糟
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.67,0:23:03.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天哪 饶了我吧
